exit
-> "exit" -> close
-> " exit" -> close
-> "exit " -> close
-> " exit " -> close
-> "exit 123" -> treat like "other text"

history
-> "history" -> print full history
-> " history" -> print full history
-> "history " -> print full history
-> " history " -> print full history
-> "history 123" -> treat like "other text"

other text:
-> [line of text] -> [word count, word=sequence of non space/newline chars] [char count, w/o spaces]
-> [empty line] -> get new line w/o doing nothing 
-> [only spaces] -> get new line w/o doing nothing
-> [line length > MAX_LINE_LENGTH] -> treat the first MAX_LINE_LENGTH - 1 chars

